title: If you haven't watched the URFitational yet you should
body:
30 seconds in and already laughing so hard at Phreak trying to hold a teacup

Riot you've done it again

EDIT: Nvm completely lost it at Dyrus in a bow tie

EDIT 2: Make sure you watch to the very, very, very end.  Also, anyone know why no C9 guys were involved?  They got a lot of the other teams in there, even EU, but no C9?
